{{#is_alert}}

## What's happening?
NiFi host {{host.name}} has one or more invalid processors.

Invalid processors cannot process data and will break any flow that depends on them. Open the NiFi UI to identify the invalid processors and resolve their configuration issues.

{{/is_alert}}

{{#is_recovery}}
All processors on NiFi host {{host.name}} are now valid.
{{/is_recovery}}
